=== Complement-Based Subgroup Stratification

Maya et al.\ (2026) identified a complement pQTL-defined inflammatory subgroup in ME/CFS with a high C3/low Bb profile, validated against UK Biobank fatigue phenotypes Complement protein levels (C3, C4, Bb, C3a, C5a) could serve as a stratification biomarker to identify patients who may benefit from complement-targeted interventions. The genetic basis of the finding (pQTLs) suggests this is a stable trait rather than a transient state.


